casebody.data:
Daniel Eric COBBLE, petitioner,
v.
Stanley WILLIAMS, Warden, et al. No. 12-8887. Supreme Court of the United States April 29, 2013.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Superior Court of Georgia, Tattnall County, dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
